SUMMARY:Information: WEMBLEY CENTRAL STATION: Friday 12\, Saturday 13\, 
 Wednesday 17\, Friday 19\, Saturday 20\, Tuesday 23\, Friday 26\, Saturday
  27\, Monday 29 June\, Wednesday 1\, Friday 3 and Saturday 4 July\, the 
 station will be busy due to concerts at Wembley Stadium. The main High 
 Road entrance will be exit only until the queue to enter the station 
 clears. If you require step-free access to the platforms\, please ask a 
 member of staff. Main entry to the station will be via the London Road 
 events entrance which is not step-free.
END:VEVENT
